text: Maximilian Pilger (born 25 February 1996) is a German swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:German male swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Swimmers at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
